item.title: Long Live The King - AstroFisiks [WIP, Project]
item.dc:creator: paxman
item.description:
I thought it was really cool how you got the delayed piano to go down in pitch slightly. Only thing I would suggest is equalizing the synths and adding lowpass/editing the volume of them to smooth out the song and make it easier to listen to at higher volumes. Keep up the good work man, you definitely got potential.
